title: Rocket Lab completes final tests on reusable 'Hungry Hippo' fairing ahead of 1st Neutron rocket launch
description: Rocket Lab has signed a contract to launch its new Neutron rocket on a test flight that will advance the U.S. Air Force's point-to-point cargo transportation concept.
